N:agentation D:"Capture exact rendered-UI feedback and hand it to an agent as selectors, element paths, and structured annotation packets. Use when a human needs to point at a real UI issue, run a sync/watch loop, or wire browser feedback into Claude Code, Codex, Gemini CLI, or OpenCode. Not for fresh-session browser verification (browser-harness), running-browser reuse (playwriter), or plan/diff approval (plannotator)." T:Read|Write|Bash|Grep|Glob P:planning-review/agentation G:ui-feedback|browser-annotation|visual-feedback|mcp|react|ai-agent|design-review|css-selector